<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Banned</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #d9534f; }
        .content p { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Account Suspension Notice
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We are writing to inform you that your Amora Hub account has been banned due to a violation of our community guidelines or terms of service.</p>
            <p>If you believe this was a mistake, please contact our support team at <strong>hub.amora@gmail.com</strong>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Amora Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>